87
00:03:58,898 --> 00:03:59,657
Wait, Lin Tao.

88
00:04:03,097 --> 00:04:05,178
Didn't you let this go already?

89
00:04:05,338 --> 00:04:06,697
What? You were faking it?

90
00:04:08,138 --> 00:04:09,377
