(Balance Sheet)

124
00:05:51,778 --> 00:05:52,577
But today,

125
00:05:52,577 --> 00:05:54,017
you must make a decision.

126
00:05:55,178 --> 00:05:56,178
Right now.

127
00:05:57,058 --> 00:05:57,778
Or else,

128
00:05:58,337 --> 00:05:59,418
