129
00:06:03,618 --> 00:06:04,418
As long as you

130
00:06:06,098 --> 00:06:07,178
promise me

131
00:06:07,577 --> 00:06:08,897
that my sister

132
00:06:09,178 --> 00:06:10,298
and Yan Studio

133
00:06:10,298 --> 00:06:11,337
