211
00:11:20,617 --> 00:11:21,298
I know.

212
00:11:22,937 --> 00:11:24,617
Your father greatly influenced you.

213
00:11:27,058 --> 00:11:27,817
You know.

214
00:11:32,138 --> 00:11:32,817
Since childhood,

215
00:11:32,817 --> 00:11:34,857
